    "Id": "chassisdef_fire_wasp_FWSP_C",
    "Name": "Fire Wasp",
    "Details": "The Fire Wasp C is the Clan rebuild of the original design, replacing every system with Clan-spec equivalents. A faster XL engine and seven jump jets push mobility beyond the already impressive original, with MASC available for emergency bursts to 140 kph. Medium Pulse Lasers replace the standard versions and the Streak SRM 2 grows to a 4-tube launcher, delivering meaningfully more damage output while keeping the same aggressive harassment identity intact.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Narrow/Low Profile</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1</color></b>",
